 <datafield tag="245" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
  <subfield code="a">A regularisation approach to causality theory for $C^{1,1}$ -Lorentzian metrics</subfield>
  <subfield code="9">Springer</subfield>
 </datafield>
 <datafield tag="520" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
  <subfield code="a">We show that many standard results of Lorentzian causality theory remain valid if the regularity of the metric is reduced to $C^{1,1}$ . Our approach is based on regularisations of the metric adapted to the causal structure.</subfield>
  <subfield code="9">Springer</subfield>
 </datafield>
